<div id="outline-container-orga935def" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga935def">du</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orga935def">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-sh"><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">## </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">##########################################################</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">directory size:  du -sh &lt;dir_name&gt; </span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">disk  usage :</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">## </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">##########################################################</span>

du -sh asia  <span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">-s : summarize , # -h : human readable</span>
du -sh sat
du -sh * <span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">size in current directory</span>
du -sh *.jpg <span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">size of all jpg formate</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">du -h Gitabase</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">378M  Gitabase</span>

</pre>
</div>

<p>
Real time  problem  <br />
There is error in code deploy and error is docker pull ecr<sub>url</sub>/repo<sub>name</sub>:latest  <br />
</p>

<p>
The error is insuffient file size unable to pull img &gt; Check there is most of file size is utilited
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-sh">du -h / 2&gt;/dev/null | grep <span style="color: #2d9574;">'[0-9\.]\+G'</span>


<span style="color: #3a81c3;">cd</span> / &amp;&amp; du -hs * | sort -rh | head -10
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">7.2G  var   # here size is more because of docker images are stored here</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">2.1G  usr   # python is installed here </span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">1.4G  snap</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">134M  boot</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">19M   opt</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">6.1M  etc</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">848K  run</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">60K   tmp</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">56K   root</span>
<span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;"># </span><span style="color: #2aa1ae; background-color: #ecf3ec;">40K   home</span>


