</pre>

<p>
Reason's for packet loss
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Network COngestion</li>
<li>Fault hardware, Cable Fault</li>
<li>Modem, or Router</li>
</ul>

<pre class="example">
$ping 192.168.1.11
