<div id="outline-container-org3ff204c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org3ff204c">Assignment</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org3ff204c">
</div>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><a id="orga637a77"></a>47) Write a command that will look for files with an extension "c", and has the occurrence of the string "apple" in it.<br />
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-orga637a77">
<p>
Answer:
</p>
<blockquote>
<p>
Find ./ -name "*.c" | xargs grep –i "apple"
</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
</li>

<li><a id="org4dc9c36"></a>48) Write a command that will display all .txt files, including its individual permission.<br />
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-org4dc9c36">
<p>
Answer:
</p>
<pre class="example">
ls -al *.txt
</pre>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
